63
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:41,860
Tusuk konde ini dari giok nefrit.

64
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,700
Barang bagus
dari Kediaman Pangeran.

65
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,040
